title: iPad & iPhone User 71 - March 2013
description:
iPad & iPhone User 71 - March 2013

68 Pages | HQ PDF | English | 9 MB 


Pad & iPhone User covers the best apps and iOS games, the latest accessories, from headphones to speaker docks and cases, and the hottest gadgets. Each issue features extensive reviews, news and opinions on the latest iPad and iPhone products, as well as step-by-step guides and tutorials on how to get the most from your Apple devices and the App Store.
